{"tid":879060,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發奇想]如果人可以植入晶片應該植喺邊？","createTime":"2018-10-27T15:39:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T18:41:18.000Z","uid":200914,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fc47ae5933d9f2456f01b3da291ac3096552a15c","tid":879060,"uid":200914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T15:39:58.000Z","msg":"話說小妹最易整唔見嘅嘢大概就係八達通同埋學生卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最高記錄大概係去一次旅行整唔見三張車飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近又整唔見咗張學生證，所以小妹最近係到諗，如果人可以以植入晶片嘅方法嚟用一啲常用嘅卡，應該植係邊到最好？<br />\n植入個頭，咁要嘟嗰時咪要成個頭冚落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟住detector咪舊舊都人咁高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n植入隻手，好似唔錯但隻手成日郁應該會好易整壞？<br />\n<br />\n開開下post又突然諗起啲狗仔都會植入晶片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"790678ee7192eac12f2a4f2129edfcb22fd5adab","tid":879060,"uid":111322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T15:41:43.000Z","msg":"心口 用對波去嘟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b28c94b8b696db188bd5df6578ef1f43e85ab4c","tid":879060,"uid":200914,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"790678ee7192eac12f2a4f2129edfcb22fd5adab","tid":879060,"uid":111322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T15:41:43.000Z","msg":"心口 用對波去嘟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T15:42:50.000Z","msg":"如果墊太厚....<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea5b95874c4d8970feab0df1e002cc90d21141f1","tid":879060,"uid":177089,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T16:07:32.000Z","msg":"個閪"},{"pid":"29887d85d854040d04e207a1252b8a5d482bb4a6","tid":879060,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T16:20:36.000Z","msg":"左手"},{"pid":"daa773399c9f0b3393095f23e2d